<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>RADService</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RADService<sp/>contains<sp/>deployment-oriented<sp/>helpers:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>systemd<sp/>unit<sp/>generation<sp/>and<sp/>writing,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>sd_notify-compatible<sp/>ready/watchdog<sp/>messages<sp/>without<sp/>libsystemd,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>single-instance<sp/>process<sp/>locks<sp/>via<sp/>`RADCore::RADLockFile`,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>optional<sp/>Unix<sp/>daemonization<sp/>for<sp/>service-style<sp/>programs.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">These<sp/>helpers<sp/>are<sp/>useful<sp/>for<sp/>embedded<sp/>appliances<sp/>and<sp/>desktop<sp/>background<sp/>tools</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">that<sp/>need<sp/>reproducible<sp/>service<sp/>metadata.</highlight></codeline>
    </programlisting>
